overview: A crackdown by the police is always just as pleasant when it is carried out by a horny, female constable who, baton in fist, brusquely forces her way into her female prisoner. Nor has anyone ever complained about a visit from two horny nurses, with Nora Nord in charge. Natalie and Jane, on the other hand, are hosted by the gardener's boy. And little Tanja, who got a new job, had no idea what helpful companions and exhaustive tasks she had been given.
title: Mmm ... Please Enter Said the Girl
